# Netlify Redirects for GadgetPro
# 1. Proxy all /api requests to the Render backend
/api/*  https://gadgetpro-naoq.onrender.com/api/:splat  200

# 2. Proxy all /uploads requests to the Render backend (for product images)
/uploads/*  https://gadgetpro-naoq.onrender.com/uploads/:splat  200

# 3. Handle React Router (SPA) - redirect all other paths to index.html
/*  /index.html  200
